<A>__{henry looks over. the guy, bill, shows him the article.}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{what about him?}
<C>__{bill}
<P>__{(reading)}
<D>__{the controversial and reclusive american poet simon grim has been awarded the nobel prize in literature. the swedish academy, who will confer the award late next week, praised mr grim for works of great and difficult striving, for the rendering of the desperate, the ugly and the mundane in a language packed with our shared human frailties...}
<C>__{henry}
<D>__{god, they must be hard up for geniuses to pin medals on because, listen, i gotta tell you, when i first met this guy he didn't even know what an iambic pentameter was.}
